    public ResponseEntity<ConvertedDatatablesData<TaskTracking>> EmployeesItemTaskTrackingsThymeleafController.datatablesByIdsIn(@RequestParam("ids") List<Long> ids, DatatablesColumns datatablesColumns, GlobalSearch search, DatatablesPageable pageable, @RequestParam("draw") Integer draw) {
        
        Page<TaskTracking> taskTrackings = getTaskTrackingService().findAllByIdsIn(ids, search, pageable);
        long totalTaskTrackingsCount = taskTrackings.getTotalElements();
        ConvertedDatatablesData<TaskTracking> data =  new ConvertedDatatablesData<TaskTracking>(taskTrackings, totalTaskTrackingsCount, draw, getConversionService(), datatablesColumns);
        return ResponseEntity.ok(data);
    }
    
